{"ts":"2026-03-08T17:13:28.000Z","author":"maintainer-agent","op":"create","patch":[{"op":"replace","path":"/body","value":"Dependency path for minimatch: c8 -> test-exclude -> minimatch (9.x had ReDoS in pattern matching). Fixed by updating to c8 v11 which uses test-exclude v8 which depends on minimatch v10.\\n\\nDependency path for rollup: vitest -> @vitest/mocker -> vite -> rollup (4.57.1 had arbitrary file write via path traversal). Fixed by adding pnpm.overrides rollup >= 4.59.0.\\n\\nBoth are devDependencies and do not affect the published npm package or end users."},{"op":"add","path":"/front_matter/id","value":"pm-r3fi"},{"op":"add","path":"/front_matter/title","value":"Fix devDependency security vulnerabilities via c8 and rollup updates"},{"op":"add","path":"/front_matter/description","value":"Update c8 from v10 to v11 (fixes minimatch ReDoS vulnerabilities in test-exclude) and add pnpm.overrides for rollup >=4.59.0 (fixes Rollup path traversal CVE via vitest -> vite -> rollup chain). All 17 Dependabot alerts resolved."},{"op":"add","path":"/front_matter/type","value":"Chore"},{"op":"add","path":"/front_matter/status","value":"closed"},{"op":"add","path":"/front_matter/priority","value":0},{"op":"add","path":"/front_matter/tags","value":["area:ci","maintenance","pm-cli","release-readiness","security"]},{"op":"add","path":"/front_matter/created_at","value":"2026-03-08T17:13:28.000Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/front_matter/updated_at","value":"2026-03-08T17:13:28.000Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/front_matter/deadline","value":"2026-03-09T17:13:28.000Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/front_matter/author","value":"maintainer-agent"},{"op":"add","path":"/front_matter/estimated_minutes","value":30},{"op":"add","path":"/front_matter/acceptance_criteria","value":"{\"id\":\"AC-1\",\"text\":\"pnpm audit reports no known vulnerabilities\",\"type\":\"security\",\"verification\":\"automated\"}"},{"op":"add","path":"/front_matter/why_now","value":"Dependabot alerts found after push to main